02/01/84  add_anon

Syntax:  add_anon Project_id initproc homedir {password}


Function: allows an accounting administrator to add an anonymous user
to an undelegated project.  He assigns this user a home directory and
an initial procedure and can also assign a password if he wishes.


Arguments:
Project_id
   is the name of the project under which the anonymous user is to be
   registered.
initproc
   is the name of the process overseer.
homedir
   is the pathname of the anonymous user's home directory.
password
   is the password assigned to the anonymous user.
